<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Quetzaat</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/algoliasearch@3.32.1/dist/algoliasearchLite.js" integrity="sha256-pMaJf0I78weeXGkRMBDO6jSulxC/q3sb0aPdtV2N8n0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/instantsearch.js@3.2.0" integrity="sha256-/8usMtTwZ01jujD7KAZctG0UMk2S2NDNirGFVBbBZCM=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=default,Array.prototype.find,Array.prototype.includes"></script>


    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/instantsearch.css@7.1.1/themes/algolia-min.css" integrity="sha256-nkldBwBn2NQqRL1mod7BqHsJ6cEOn6u/ln6F/lI4CFo=" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://npmcdn.com/flickity@2/dist/flickity.css">
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar is-info">
      <div class="navbar-brand">
        <%= link_to root_path do %>
          <h1 class="has-text-centered title is-1 has-text-white">Quetzaat</h1>
        <% end %>
        <a role="button" class="navbar-burger" data-target="navMenu" aria-label="menu" aria-expanded="false">
          <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="navbar-menu" id="navMenu">
        <div class="navbar-end">
          <% if(user_signed_in?) %>
            <%= link_to "Agregar producto", new_product_path, class: "navbar-item" %>
            <%= link_to "Mis pedidos", "/orders", class: "navbar-item" %>
            <div class="navbar-item has-dropdown is-hoverable">
              <a class="navbar-link">
                Categorias
              </a>
              <div class="navbar-dropdown">
                <a class="navbar-item">
                  Ropa
                </a>
                <a class="navbar-item">
                  Regalos
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="navbar-item">Ofertas</a>
            <%= link_to "Acerca de", "/about", class: "navbar-item" %>
            <%= link_to "Cerrar sesión", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "navbar-item" %>
          <% else %>
            <%= link_to "Registrarse", new_user_registration_path, class: "navbar-item" %>
            <%= link_to "Iniciar Sesión", new_user_session_path, class: "navbar-item" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <script src="https://npmcdn.com/flickity@2/dist/flickity.pkgd.js"></script>
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns column-footer">
          <div class="column">
            <h3 class="subtitle is-3">E-Commerce</h3>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Alias debitis deleniti deserunt earum enim hic, laborum nemo optio placeat praesentium quasi reiciendis, rem repellat sed sint velit veniam vero voluptates!</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorem ipsum iusto modi molestias nihil odit tempore temporibus. Adipisci at aut beatae consequuntur explicabo fugit harum inventore iure possimus quae! Veritatis!</p>

            <hr class="spacer">

            <div class="tag is-link">Facebook</div>
            <div class="tag is-danger">YouTube</div>
            <div class="tag is-info">Twitter</div>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3712.5549406281184!2d-101.21985243992764!3d21.485972854116998!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0xfb059c8668e7f7d5!2sMonumento+al+Indio!5e0!3m2!1ses!2smx!4v1554738391754!5m2!1ses!2smx" width="600" height="750" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="has-text-centered has-text-black">Todos los derechos reservados &copycopyright Quetzaan.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
